channel.title: Development Customs On DSPK [PI]
channel.description:
[center]Hi Recently i've noticed that there wasn't really Customs on DSPK, People say People Don't Want Customs for DSPK, but i have proof they do. In the first month (still in my first month) my total players at its peak was 62. We regularly have 36-47 now. The name is Myth-Scape And These are the customs i've made so far, there are definetly more here to come. [u][b]I would also like to know what Customs you think would be cool to add to Dspk, post as a reply[/b][/u]
[IMG]http://i1047.photobucket.com/albums/b479/jackhopson/customs.png[/img]
I'm willing to help anybody with Customs. And if requested enough i'll release a tut, I would definetly Tell you to follow I Vain I's Tutorial on how to do this, but as you can see i was able to add recolors and customs. Add my Msn if you want XD: Mythscape@live.com[/center]
